    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_jc.00578_large.jpg" type="recto"/> 
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden<ptr target="loc.03933_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1887-08-01">Monday Evn'g Aug 1</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>We have had three hot days right in a string but I am getting along with it all,
                &#38; there is a great let up evenings &#38; nights&#8212;Nobody here to day&#8212;I
                think of you &#38; George<ptr target="loc.03933_n2"/> &#38; all&#8212;H<ptr
                    target="n0590"/> yesterday told me he was much better&#8212;good&#8212;I will be
                down one of these days&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc_jc.00577_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
